name: "Kindness"
description:
This minimalistic piece was minted on HEN in the spring at the very beginning of my journey in NFT. When I came back after a long summer break (mental health), I burned this piece.

 
Now after the events related to Hicetnunc, I would like to bring him back here. Because I like this work and I like the kindness that I see in the art community on Tezos.

3000×3000px,
lyamovie, 2021
